# Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` for local development.
These variables MUST also be set in your Vercel project dashboard under Settings → Environment Variables.

```
# Your Resend API key — get it free at https://resend.com
RESEND_API_KEY=re_d5z9P9dc_3QzqDavXVQYBiAhXuMhwKkLz

# The email address that will RECEIVE demo booking notifications
NOTIFICATION_EMAIL=oyenolaphilip89@gmail.com

# The sender email — must be a domain you've verified in Resend
# You can use the default Resend sandbox: onboarding@resend.dev (no verification needed for testing)
SENDER_EMAIL=onboarding@resend.dev
```
